 polarization effects in the presence of gravitation are\npointed out and the extension to Fock bundles of bosonic and fermionic type is\nbriefly mentioned.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Oct 1996 16:15:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-07-19"}
